OL,3,CAre Holiday homes being mis-sold with
OL,4,Cbuyers misled?
OL,6,FAcross Britain many of us have fond
OL,7,Fmemories of caravan holidays, packing
OL,8,Fup and heading off on well-deserved
OL,9,Ftrips to relax and recharge. It's big
OL,10,Fbusiness too, the UK is home to around
OL,11,Ffour and a half thousand holiday parks
OL,12,Fand with over a hundred and fifty
OL,13,Fthousand holiday caravans, for many
OL,14,Fthe thought of owning one is a dream,
OL,15,Fbut what seems like the perfect
OL,16,Flifestyle can turn into a costly
OL,17,Fregret.
