OL,3,CAre Holiday homes being mis-sold with
OL,4,Cbuyers misled?
OL,6,FPeople across the country who have
OL,7,Fpurchased caravans on holiday parks
OL,8,Fhave reported losing significant
OL,9,Famounts of money, amid allegations of
OL,10,Fquestionable sales tactics, rapid
OL,11,Fdepreciation and hidden fees. It is
OL,12,Fbeing described by some as a national
OL,13,Fscandal.
OL,15,FHow has this happened, and what can be
OL,16,Fdone to protect consumers? Michelle
OL,17,FAckerley has been investigating.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
