OL,3,CAre Holiday homes being mis-sold with
OL,4,Cbuyers misled?
OL,6,FThere is some hope though; across the
OL,7,Fcountry thousands of consumers have
OL,8,Fnow joined together to bring group
OL,9,Flegal action to the high courts. The
OL,10,FHoliday Park Action Group started in
OL,11,F2019 and has amassed more than 70,000
OL,12,Fmembers on its Facebook Page.
OL,14,FTonight spoke to the Barrister
OL,15,Frepresenting the group, Hugh Preston
OL,16,FKC.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
