OL,3,CAre Holiday homes being mis-sold with
OL,4,Cbuyers misled?
OL,6,F"The legal action is focusing on two
OL,7,Fissues, the lack of transparency about
OL,8,Fthe risks that the consumers are
OL,9,Ftaking, and the annual pitch fees that
OL,10,Fare charged on parks, they can
OL,11,Fsometimes really get out of control."
OL,12,F- Hugh Preston KC
