OL,3,CAre Holiday homes being mis-sold with
OL,4,Cbuyers misled?
OL,6,FThe next stage for the legal action
OL,7,Fwill be for the High Court to rule on
OL,8,Fa series of test cases. Around 2,500
OL,9,Fpeople are pursuing this legal route.
OL,10,FIt is operating on a 'no win no fee'
OL,11,Fbasis, meaning those who apply are
OL,12,Fprotected financially, but it applies
OL,13,Fonly to people who bought their
OL,14,Fholiday home with a loan or finance
OL,15,Fagreement, not those who paid upfront
OL,16,Fwith cash.
