OL,3,CAre Holiday homes being mis-sold with
OL,4,Cbuyers misled?
OL,6,FThe British Holiday & Home Parks
OL,7,FAssociation who represent the industry
OL,8,Ftold Tonight: "Buying a holiday
OL,9,Fcaravan or lodge is a long-term
OL,10,Flifestyle purchase, not a financial
OL,11,Finvestment. It is designed to enable
OL,12,Fyou to enjoy regular holidays for a
OL,13,Ffixed period of time ` usually 10
OL,14,Fyears or more. Its value will fall
OL,15,Fover time with the greatest reduction
OL,16,Fcoming in the short term, i.e. if you
OL,17,Fend the contract within the first year
OL,18,For two". They also said they've made
OL,19,Fan information video for people
OL,20,Flooking to buy a holiday home, which
OL,21,Fcan be found on their website.
